Creating Telecom Revenue for 2017 Dashboard

        ·         To make it easy, provided the Tableau Packaged workbook for Dashboard with first few steps.

        ·        Download the Workbook from Data file. This workbook contains all the prior steps that we did and few Steps for creating Dashboard.

        ·        Make Sure Object is in Floating. Or Else In object Click Floating

        

        ·         Drag and Drop Sheets one by one that you want from Sheets. Here I dragged and Dropped Top 10 Spenders.

        ·         I showed for One Sheet (Top 10 Spenders). Similarly arrange remaining Sheets to Create the Dashboard.

        ·         Make Use of Grid Lines (Small Checked box) to arrange the Sheets properly.

        

        ·         Right Click on Title (Top 10 Spenders) and make it to Center. If Title is already in Center ignore next two steps.

        

        ·         Another Wizard will pop up. In that, Select Sheet Name ---- > Choose Center ---- > Click Apply ---- > Click Ok

        

        ·         Arrange the Sheet in Dashboard by Dragging the bottom line (Keep the Cursor at bottom line of Visualization and Drag).Similarly, for enlarging the Visualization Place the Cursor on Side line and Drag .

        

        ·         To move the Visualization either to Top or Bottom to Center, Click and Drag the lines at top of Visualization like below.

        

         ·         Dashboard like below will appear. Similarly arrange all the remaining sheets.

         

        ·         Once arranged all the Sheets, Click Dashboard at top and Click Show Grid Lines.

        

        ·         Dashboard like below will appear.

        

        ·         To See in Presentation mode Click on fn + F7 button in Dashboard Page.

        ·         This is Final Dashboard for Telecom Revenue for 2017
